.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-PIN-RESET" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-pin-reset \- remove PIN protection from a wallet
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-pin-reset
.I wallet_name
.SH DESCRIPTION
Clears the stored PIN hash and attempt counter from the wallet database.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"status":"pin_reset","wallet":"<name>"}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-pin-set (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-pin-check (1)
